Belgian woman Els Clottemans is sentenced to 30 years imprisonment for murdering her love rival Els Van Doren by sabotaging her parachute so neither it nor a safety chute would open during a November 18, 2006 parachute jump. (Fox News)Files on the death of British biological weapons inspector David Kelly, which had previously been kept secret by the British government for 7 years, are released, stating that his wounds were typical of "self-inflicted injury". (The Telegraph) (RTÉ)Gunmen kill thirteen people and wound fifteen at a birthday party in the Mexican border city of Ciudad Juárez. (Al Jazeera) (Reuters)